Currently the view mapping is quite simple. Its just a list of concepts bridging the database schema mapping to the view mapping:

[[%ATTACHURL%/2stepmapping.jpg][2stepmapping.jpg]]

To allow for smarter wrappers, the view mapping could include more information:

   * EntityMapping, mapping abstract "classes" and not only properties of classes.


